FBIS3-13326 "drnes049_p_94002" FBIS-NES-94-049 Document Type:Daily Report 14 Mar 1994 SOUTH ASIA Afghanistan Islamabad Reports `Fierce Fighting' in North BK1103144294 Islamabad PTV Television Network in English 1400 GMT 11 Mar 94 BK1103144294 Islamabad PTV Television Network Language: English Article Type:BFN [Text] Fierce fighting between the rival factions has been reported in northern Afghanistan, including some parts of Baghlan Province. Government and opposition warplanes bombarded each other's positions in Baghlan Province.
